      <title>积分平台之十一[账号归档]</title>
      <link>https://yongqiangg.github.io/zh/posts/tech/%E7%A7%AF%E5%88%86%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E4%B9%8B%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E8%B4%A6%E5%8F%B7%E5%BD%92%E6%A1%A3/</link>
